  "pages": [
    {
      "type": "patchouli:text",
      "text": "七彩基座和融合圣坛虽然各显神通，但都仍有相当大的改进空间。为此，你设计了这些增益器。每种增益器各为结构本身的某项功能提供特化加成，选取哪种悉听尊便。$(br)同类增益器效果叠加，但加成递减。"
    },


    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "advancement": "spectrum:midgame/build_advanced_pedestal_structure",
      "title": "合成加速器",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier3/upgrade_speed",
      "text": "处理复杂原料时，$(l:general/pedestal)七彩基座$(/l)的合成用时会变得相当长久。合成加速器能把耗时压入可以接受的时长内。"
    },
    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "advancement": "spectrum:progression/unlock_upgrade_speed2",
      "title": "II级升级",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier3/upgrade_speed2",
      "text": "II级合成加速器是前者的全面升级，助你更快速地合成物品。"
    },
    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "advancement": "spectrum:progression/unlock_upgrade_speed3",
      "title": "III级升级",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier4/upgrade_speed3",
      "text": "III级升级，无忧无虑——至少在合成速率上确实不会再有什么顾虑了。"
    },

    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "advancement": "spectrum:progression/unlock_upgrade_experience",
      "title": "知识汇集器",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier3/upgrade_experience",
      "text": "$(l:general/pedestal)七彩基座$(/l)合成生产的经验经常只够塞牙缝。知识汇集器能够可观地提高经验产量。"
    },
    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "advancement": "spectrum:progression/unlock_upgrade_experience2",
      "title": "II级升级",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier3/upgrade_experience2",
      "text": "升级版知识汇集器还能再进一步提高产量。"
    },

    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "advancement": "spectrum:midgame/create_refined_azurite",
      "title": "反应催化器",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier3/upgrade_efficiency",
      "text": "$(l:general/pedestal)七彩基座$(/l)对宝石晶粉末的消耗可谓狮子大开口。$(br)现在总算能节流了，能省一点是一点。"
    },
    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "advancement": "spectrum:progression/unlock_upgrade_efficiency2",
      "title": "II级升级",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier4/upgrade_efficiency2",
      "text": "这款“升级的增益”还能再多精省一点资源。"
    },

    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "advancement": "spectrum:lategame/collect_paletur",
      "title": "转化率提升器",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier4/upgrade_yield",
      "text": "这个有意思。你有几率获得更多的合成产物，虽然概率很小。$(br)$(italic)物美价廉，单车变摩托啦！"
    },
    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "advancement": "spectrum:progression/unlock_upgrade_yield2",
      "title": "II级升级",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier4/upgrade_yield2",
      "text": "升级版则是更为强劲，你可能获得更多产物。"
    },

